---
---
<section class="testimonials-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2>Don't Just Take Our Word For It</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Join thousands of others who have reclaimed their peace of mind.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="testimonial-card glass-panel">
        <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
        <p class="quote">"Before this, I felt constantly drained. I thought I was just burnt out. After applying the shielding techniques from module 2, the heavy feeling lifted overnight. It's like I finally have my life back."</p>
        <div class="author">
          <div class="author-avatar" style="background-image: url('https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/44.jpg')"></div>
          <div>
            <h4>Sarah M.</h4>
            <span class="verified">✓ Verified Member</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="testimonial-card glass-panel">
        <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
        <p class="quote">"The community alone is worth 10x the price. Being around others who actually understand what spiritual stalking feels like is so validating. The techniques are just the icing on the cake."</p>
        <div class="author">
          <div class="author-avatar" style="background-image: url('https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/32.jpg')"></div>
          <div>
            <h4>David K.</h4>
            <span class="verified">✓ Verified Member</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="testimonial-card glass-panel">
        <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
        <p class="quote">"I was skeptical at first, but the step-by-step approach to cord-cutting actually worked for me when nothing else did. I sleep through the night now. Thank you!"</p>
        <div class="author">
          <div class="author-avatar" style="background-image: url('https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/68.jpg')"></div>
          <div>
            <h4>Elena R.</h4>
            <span class="verified">✓ Verified Member</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(var(--primary-rgb), 0.05), transparent 70%);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-desc {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100%;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: transform var(--transition-smooth);
  }

  .testimonial-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .stars {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .quote {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .author-avatar {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }

  .author h4 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .mb-12 { margin-bottom: 3rem; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .testimonials-section { padding: 4rem 0; }
    .testimonials-grid { gap: 1.5rem; }
    .testimonial-card { padding: 1.5rem; }
    .quote { font-size: 1.05rem; }
  }
</style>
